                'J': '您是个靠谱的规划大师，对风险把控有着近乎苛刻的追求。有您在的项目，总能有条不紊地按时甚至提前高品质交付。',
                'P': '您拥有极强的环境适应力和灵活的应变手腕。在充满未知的高压局面中，总能捕捉转机，展现出惊人的逆商和爆发力。'
            };

            const weakZh = {
                'E': '您有时会过度沉浸于表达自我，容易忽视倾听他人的深层诉求。处理长周期枯燥任务时，容易感到烦躁并出现疏漏。',
                'I': '过于内敛的特质往往导致才华被掩盖。在需要据理力争或向上争取资源时，您的退缩会让团队错失良机并产生距离感。',
                'S': '由于过度依赖过往经验和安全规则，面对大规模行业变革时可能显得迟钝，对极具潜力的创新事物存在本能排斥。',
                'N': '常常沉醉于构思宏大愿景，却容易对落地执行的艰辛视而不见。若缺乏对现实资源和细节的考量，极易造成项目虎头蛇尾。',
                'T': '对效率的极度追求，常让您在沟通中显得过于冷酷不留情面。对“低效行为”的零容忍，可能会刺伤队友的自尊与积极性。',
                'F': '极易受周遭负面情绪感染。在面临需要“快刀斩乱麻”的业务切割时，往往因过度顾及他人感受而变得优柔寡断。',
                'J': '对绝对秩序的病态迷恋，使得面对突发计划变更或插队时，易产生极大挫败感与焦虑。僵化的流程思维有时会扼杀灵活性。',
                'P': '随性而为的工作节奏，常让配合您的上下游同事缺乏安全感。重度拖延症和对 deadlines 的极限试探，随时可能引发连锁反应。'
            };

            const strEn = {
                'E': 'You radiate a strong energy field, easily driving team atmosphere and navigating cross-departmental communication as a natural speaker.',
                'I': 'You possess intense independent thinking, maintaining extreme calm in chaos. Peeling back complex problems is your forte.',
                'S': 'Grounded and highly sensitive to data and details. You flawlessly translate grand strategies into executable SOPs.',
                'N': 'You possess visionary strategic insight and keen innovative instincts, always stepping out of conventional frameworks.',
                'T': 'With tight underlying logic, your decisions are rarely clouded by emotion. You weigh pros and cons decisively.',
                'F': 'You have outstanding empathy and interpersonal connection, naturally binding the team together and boosting morale.',
                'J': 'As a reliable planning master, you strictly control risks and time, ensuring projects are delivered systematically.',
                'P': 'You show incredible adaptability and flexibility. In high-pressure, unknown situations, you capture turning points brilliantly.'
            };

            const weakEn = {
                'E': 'You may over-indulge in self-expression, neglecting others\' deeper needs. Long, tedious tasks easily frustrate you.',
                'I': 'Your reserved nature might hide your true talents. Hesitation in fighting for resources can make you appear distant.',
                'S': 'Over-relying on past experience might make you slow to adapt to massive industry shifts, instinctively resisting novelties.',
                'N': 'Fascinated by grand visions, you may overlook the hardships of execution, leading to projects that start strong but fade out.',
                'T': 'Your extreme pursuit of efficiency can make you seem ruthlessly cold, potentially hurting teammates\' enthusiasm.',
                'F': 'Easily drained by surrounding negativity. You may become indecisive when tough business cuts are necessary.',
                'J': 'Your obsession with order creates severe anxiety when facing sudden plan changes. Rigid thinking can kill flexibility.',
                'P': 'Your casual pace strips security from colleagues. Severe procrastination and testing deadlines risk chain-reaction failures.'
